OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud thinning and breaking,
OL,6,Fperhaps allowing the odd brighter
OL,7,Fspell, especially toward the north.
OL,8,FHowever, thicker cloud in the south
OL,9,Fcould give some patchy rain for much
OL,10,Fof the day. Light winds. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining largely cloudy
OL,13,Fthrough the evening and overnight, as
OL,14,Frain gradually clears the south.
OL,15,FOutbreaks of rain possible over
OL,16,Fwestern hills later. Light winds.
OL,17,FFrost possible in rural parts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
