OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloud thinning and breaking
OL,6,Fon Saturday morning, turning brighter
OL,7,Fbefore a band of showers progresses
OL,8,Feastward in the afternoon. An
OL,9,Fovernight frost possible in rural
OL,10,Fparts.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStrong
OL,13,Fwinds Sunday and Monday, with some
OL,14,Frain spreading east but also some
OL,15,Fdrier spells. Likely dry Tuesday with
OL,16,Flight winds and sunny spells.
OL,17,FTemperatures a little above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
